						<summary>

						<p>Stone kept near the cowshed.</p>						

						<p>This is dated <hi rend="bold">Śaka 737, Madyamaviśa Vijaya, Uttarāyaṇa-Saṅkramaṇa.</hi></p>						

						<p>Registers a gift of 150 <hi rend="italic">maruṭṭuru</hi> of land at Velmalūru by Vallava Salkalu to the god Bhōgīśvara. The gift was entrusted to Komarasamula Śivakarabhavyalu.</p>						

						</summary>
